Package KI305.Malynovskyi.Lab2

Class AudioPlayer

java.lang.Object
KI305.Malynovskyi.Lab2.AudioPlayer
All Implemented Interfaces:
AutoCloseable
public class AudioPlayer extends Object implements AutoCloseable
Class AudioPlayer models a simple audio player device.

It contains several components (engine, playlist, speaker, storage) and writes a protocol of operations to a log file.
